name: Laberinto
overview: A maze and crosshairs shooter game created for the "Posadas Party III" event in 2018. An Amiga game developed by S2N. Escape from the labyrinth before the Batmanu attack. Batmanu has locked you inside a PC. A labyrinth of evil circuits. You will have to escape through the only door there is. Run! But beware of Batmanu! It will not make it easy.
